		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I spread that wrong information. The difference I found between two different MMC3 boards wasn't attributable to the revision letter, as it was the same for both (even the date codes were a few weeks apart). The difference might have been the board itself or something else. This means we don't really know anything about the revision differences, if any.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
